ier Reef of Australia, or swim with dolphins in the Pacific Ocean\n- Relax on a beach practicing guided meditation\n- Listen to classical music\n- Play with your virtual pet\n- Change your perspective from ocean to green meadow, to snowy mountains\n\nAlcove has something for everyone, no matter your age. Download Alcove and start exploring today!\n\nNote: Alcove will keep growing with new immersive experiences and features. Please leave us a note to let us know what you\u2019d love to see next.", "short_description": "A virtual home filled with endless experiences to discover and explore, a place to connect with friends and family. Casual games, world travel, media customization, relaxation, and adventure."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.aarp.org/about-aarp/privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.aarp.org/about-aarp/terms-of-service/", "publisher_name": "AARP Innovation Labs", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://alcovevr.com/", "category": "APPS", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["EXPLORATION", "SOCIAL", "TRAVEL"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH", "HAND_TRACKING"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER", "MULTI_USER", "CO_OP"], "id": "2803101913326406"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "754019892058176"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "754019892058176"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1597942800, "status": "PUBLIS